          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1721398658556-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the chicken is cooking, add the<strong> sliced red onion</strong> to a bowl with your<strong> cider vinegar</strong>, a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>[4 tbsp] </span><strong>cold water</strong></p><p>Set aside to pickle – this is your<strong> quick-pickled onion</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1721398663152-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1721398663152-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1721398663152-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
